<section class="brand--department-for-business-innovation-skills brand__border-color organisation__brand-border-top organisation__section-wrap organisation__margin-bottom" id="what-we-do">
  <div class="grid-row">
    <div class="column-two-thirds">
      <h2 class="gem-c-heading  gem-c-heading--padding gem-c-heading--margin-bottom-2  ">What the Council for Science and Technology does</h2>

    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="grid-row">
    <div class="column-two-thirds">
      
<div class="gem-c-govspeak govuk-govspeak " data-module="govspeak">
    
          <p></p>
<div class="govspeak">
<p>The Council for Science and Technology (CST) advises the Prime Minister on science and technology policy issues which cut across the responsibilities of government departments. The council is supported by a secretariat based in the Government Office for Science.</p>

<p><abbr title="Council for Science and Technology">CST</abbr> is an advisory non-departmental public body, sponsored by the <a class="brand__color" href="/government/organisations/department-for-business-energy-and-industrial-strategy">Department for Business, Energy & Industrial Strategy</a>.</p>
</div>

          <p>
            <a href="/government/organisations/council-for-science-and-technology/about" class="brand__color">
              Read more about what we do
            </a>
          </p>

</div>
    </div>

      <div class="column-one-third">
        <h3 class="gem-c-heading  gem-c-heading--font-size-19 gem-c-heading--margin-bottom-2  ">Follow us</h3>

          <div class="gem-c-share-links brand--department-for-business-innovation-skills gem-c-share-links--stacked" data-module="track-click">

    <ul class="gem-c-share-links__list">
